<?xml version="1.0" ?>
<dialog name="Langston" displayName="Sara Sidle">
	<conversation location="CrimeScene" visit="1" name="Outside">
		<statement num="1"><![CDATA[Glad you're here.]]></statement>
		<statement num="2"><![CDATA[The victim is a young male. A female named Natalie Perez had called the fire department after escaping the fire.

The call came in around 3 am.]]></statement>
		<statement num="3"><![CDATA[She did not appear to have any severe physical injuries, but EMS did treat her for smoke inhalation and transferred her to the hospital.]]></statement>
		<statement num="4"><![CDATA[That's what we need to find out. It's important to keep an open mind when investigating a fire.]]></statement>
		<statement num="5"><![CDATA[Doc Robbins' team has already picked it up.]]></statement>
		<statement num="6"><![CDATA[First, look for evidence outside the house and see if there are any witnesses.

Then we can investigate the fire scene.]]></statement>		
		<response num="1"><![CDATA[What happened?]]></response>
		<response num="2"><![CDATA[Where is Natalie Perez now?]]></response>
		<response num="3"><![CDATA[Was it arson or an accident?]]></response>
		<response num="4"><![CDATA[Where is the body?]]></response>
		<response num="5"><![CDATA[What do I need to do?]]></response>
		<response num="6"><![CDATA[I'm ready to start investigating.]]></response>
	</conversation>
	<conversation location="CrimeScene" visit="1" name="OutsideUnfinished">
		<statement num="1"><![CDATA[Do you have any questions?]]></statement>
		<statement num="2"><![CDATA[Not yet. You still need to ]]></statement>
		<statement num="2_1"><![CDATA[search for evidence outside the house.]]></statement>
		<statement num="2_2"><![CDATA[talk to the witness.]]></statement>
		<statement num="2_3"><![CDATA[investigate the fire scene inside the house.]]></statement>
		<response num="1"><![CDATA[Am I done here?]]></response>
		<response num="2"><![CDATA[I'll keep investigating.]]></response>
	</conversation>
	<conversation location="CrimeScene" visit="1" name="OutsideFinished">
		<statement num="1"><![CDATA[Do you have any questions?]]></statement>
		<statement num="2"><![CDATA[Yes, let's go back to headquarters and analyze the evidence we have.]]></statement>
		<response num="1"><![CDATA[Am I done here?]]></response>
		<response num="2"><![CDATA[Let's go to the lab.]]></response>
	</conversation>
	<conversation location="CrimeScene_LivingRoom" visit="1" name="LivingRoom">		
		<statement num="1"><![CDATA[Do you have a question about the investigation?]]></statement>
		<statement num="2"><![CDATA[Documentation is key when investigating a fire.

You should photograph the scene and look for evidence.]]></statement>
		<statement num="3"><![CDATA[Use the camera in your tools.]]></statement>
		<statement num="4"><![CDATA[Anything that might point to the origin of the fire.

Also, look for circumstantial evidence such as personal belongings.]]></statement>	
		<response num="1"><![CDATA[What should I do here?]]></response>
		<response num="2"><![CDATA[How do I take pictures?]]></response>
		<response num="3"><![CDATA[What kind of evidence should I look for?]]></response>
		<response num="4"><![CDATA[I'll start processing the scene.]]></response>
	</conversation>
	<conversation location="CrimeScene_LivingRoom" visit="1" name="LivingRoomUnfinished">
		<statement num="1"><![CDATA[How can I help you?]]></statement>
		<statement num="2"><![CDATA[Not yet. You still need to ]]></statement>
		<statement num="2_1"><![CDATA[use your camera to photograph the scene.]]></statement>
		<statement num="2_2"><![CDATA[use your chisel to take a sample of the floor material with the puddle-shaped burn pattern.]]></statement>
		<statement num="2_3"><![CDATA[find more evidence.]]></statement>
		<statement num="2_4"><![CDATA[search for evidence outside the house.]]></statement>
		<statement num="2_5"><![CDATA[talk to the witness.]]></statement>
		<response num="1"><![CDATA[Am I done here?]]></response>
		<response num="2"><![CDATA[I'll keep investigating.]]></response>
	</conversation>
	<conversation location="CrimeScene_LivingRoom" visit="1" name="LivingRoomFinished">
		<statement num="1"><![CDATA[Do you have any questions?]]></statement>
		<statement num="2"><![CDATA[Yes, let's go back to headquarters and analyze the evidence we have.]]></statement>
		<response num="1"><![CDATA[Am I done here?]]></response>
		<response num="2"><![CDATA[Let's go to the lab.]]></response>
	</conversation>
	<conversation location="CrimeScene_LivingRoom" visit="1" name="Photos">
		<statement num="1"><![CDATA[This puddle-shaped burn pattern is suspicious. Patterns like this can occur in areas where ignitable liquids were poured on the floor.

You should take a sample of the burned wood flooring so that we can test it for ignitable liquids in the lab.]]></statement>
		<statement num="2"><![CDATA[Try to use the fire scene tool kit from your tool collection.]]></statement>
		<response num="1"><![CDATA[How can I take a sample of the flooring?]]></response>
		<response num="2"><![CDATA[I'll finish taking pictures and then take a sample.]]></response>		
	</conversation>
