	<conversation location="Hospital" visit="1" name="Hospital">
		<statement num="1"><![CDATA[Good job so far. Do you have any questions?]]></statement>
		<statement num="2"><![CDATA[You need to talk to the victim's girlfriend, Natalie Perez.

Also, ask her doctor to give you access to her patient report.]]></statement>
		<statement num="3"><![CDATA[You'll find her room in the corridor behind me.]]></statement>
		<statement num="4"><![CDATA[Her office is to your right.]]></statement>
		<statement num="5"><![CDATA[Yes - since the medical data is relevant for the case, Brass made sure your search warrant includes Natalie's patient record.]]></statement>
		<response num="1"><![CDATA[What should I do here?]]></response>
		<response num="2"><![CDATA[Where can I find Natalie Perez?]]></response>
		<response num="3"><![CDATA[Where can I find Natalie's doctor?]]></response>
		<response num="4"><![CDATA[Can I legally obtain the medical data?]]></response>
		<response num="5"><![CDATA[I'll keep investigating.]]></response>
	</conversation>
	<conversation location="Hospital" visit="1" name="HospitalUnfinished">
		<statement num="1"><![CDATA[How can I help you?]]></statement>
		<statement num="2"><![CDATA[Not yet. You still need to ]]></statement>
		<statement num="2_1"><![CDATA[talk to Dr. Lewis.]]></statement>
		<statement num="2_2"><![CDATA[take a look at Natalie's patient report.]]></statement>
		<statement num="2_3"><![CDATA[as Dr. Lewis about the patient report.]]></statement>
		<statement num="2_4"><![CDATA[access the simulation on the doctor's computer.]]></statement>
		<statement num="2_5"><![CDATA[talk to the patient, Natalie Perez.]]></statement>
		<response num="1"><![CDATA[Am I done here?]]></response>
		<response num="2"><![CDATA[I'll keep investigating.]]></response>
